          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copyright">
        <div class="container teal-text text-lighten-3">
          <strong>
            <a class="teal-text text-lighten-5" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/deed">CC BY 3.0</a> <code>::</code>
            доктрина: строю метамодели <code>::</code>
